channel.description:
I wanna add colors like @red@ "test". How i can do that?
I have added this to client.java :
[code]private static String combatDiffColor(int i, int j)
	{
		int k = i - j;
		if(k < -9)
			return "@red@";
		if(k < -6)
			return "@or3@";
		if(k < -3)
			return "@or2@";
		if(k < 0)
			return "@or1@";
		if(k > 9)
			return "@gre@";
		if(k > 6)
			return "@gr3@";
		if(k > 3)
			return "@gr2@";
		if(k > 0)
			return "@gr1@";
		else
			return "@yel@";
	}[/code]
